OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 29 MAR
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG1998FBBC America begins broadcasting.
OL,7,FThe channel is owned by BBC Studios and
OL,8,FAMC Networks and airs a mix of
OL,9,Fprogramme genres including sci-fi,
OL,10,Faction, documentaries, as well as
OL,11,Ffilms. It is funded through
OL,12,Fadvertising.
OL,13,
OL,14,CG2002FBBC One updates its on-screen
OL,15,Fpresentation. The globe device is
OL,16,Fdropped and replaced by a series of
OL,17,Flive-action idents, with the theme
OL,18,Frhythm and movement. The new package
OL,19,Fwas produced by Lambie-Nairn.
